parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine oil pressure leaks can cause engine damage, overheating, and potentially lead to engine seizure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Knocking noise coming from the engine

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure due to Header or Camshaft Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure due to header or camshaft issues can cause the engine to shut off, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
Vacuum hose failure can cause engine hesitation, loss of power, and potentially lead to engine stalling or failure.
The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the vehicle's occupants may not receive the necessary protection to prevent harm.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended deployment of airbags can cause injuries, distractions, and accidents, especially if it occurs while the vehicle is in motion.

The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to a loss of control and increased risk of accidents. In severe cases, it can also cause a fire, as reported in one instance.
symptoms: The vehicle turns off when stopped
the engine light comes on periodically
the hold and TCS lights come on
the vehicle refuses to go into overdrive
grinding sound when turning the key
loud popping noise when the key is turned again.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ECM can cause the engine to malfunction, leading to a loss of power and control, and increasing the risk of accidents. It can also cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving.
symptoms: the hold and TCS lights come on
the vehicle refuses to go into overdrive
the ECM computer needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the vehicle to have intermittent starting problems, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: Grinding sound when turning the key
loud popping noise when the key is turned again
the engine fails to turn over.
